high_descs: Head forward, turn right, go to the black shelf.
Pick up the remote on the shelf.
Bring the remote near the box on the lower shelf.
Put the remote in the box.
Pick up the box with the remote in it.
Turn around and head to the chair.
Put the box with remote on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with remote on the chair.

high_descs: Go straight, then go left to go to the shelf.
Pick up the remote from the higher shelf.
Turn down, to the lower shelf.
Place the remote in the box, on the shelf.
Pick up the box with the remote in it.
Turn around, then go straight to approach the chair.
Put the box on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box with a remote in it on the chair.

high_descs: Head forward towards the wall. Turn right, turn left, turn right and head forward towards the table.
Look up on the shelf and pick up the remote.
Step back, turn left then turn right, take another step back, look inside the box.
Place the remote into the cardboard box.
Pick up the cardboard box that the remote was placed in.
Turn around and walk towards the chair.
Place the cardboard box with the remote on the chair.
anns.task_desc: Place the box with a remote control onto the chair.

high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk across the room to the shelf on the wall.
Pick up the remote off of the shelf on the wall.
Turn left and take a step forward, then turn right and look down at the bench.
Put the remote in the cardboard box on the bench.
Pick up the cardboard box with the remote in it off of the bench.
Turn right and begin walking forward, then turn right again and walk over to the black chair in the corner of the room.
Put the cardboard box with the remote in it onto the seat of the black chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a remote in it on the seat of a black chair.

high_descs: Walk straight to the wall and then go right to the bench.
Pick up the remote from the shelf.
Turn around and then back to the box.
Put the remote into the box.
Pick up the box with the remote in it.
Turn around and take the box and remote to the chair.
Set the box and remote onto the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put away the remote into a box on the chair.

high_descs: Go to the front of the chair in front of you, then turn right and go to the opposite wall.
Take the remote control from the shelf.
Go to the cardboard box on the lower shelf in front of you.
Put the remote control in the box.
Pick up the box with the controller inside.
Turn around and return to the chair.
Put the box holding the controller on the seat of the chair.
anns.task_desc: Put a box holding a remote control on the seat of a chair.
